THIS IS THE BETA VERSION, GET THE FINAL VERSION HERE:  http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/114345
===========
===========

"de_california_beta1"

This is the first Beta version. The terrorist have to take out either the town’s ammo cache, or the town’s two main fuel tanks.  The counter-terrorists must protect both of these areas.

I want to give Lost a big thanks for helping me optimize this map, thanks a lot man! 
Lost: http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/109641

This is a BETA version.  Please give any suggestions, critical feedback, report bugs/problems in the map so that the final version can be bug free.  If you report any major bugs or big problems in the map please describe in more than a few sentences what is wrong; if you give a good Bug Report I will add your name in the “Special Thanks” section for “Testing” on the final release.

-	48 Spawns
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview Radar Map
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-	Optimized with Hint, No Draw, and Areaportals for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Custom Textures from CGTextures at www.cgtextures.com

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
